SHE_CTE (Shear Common Testing Environment)
==========================================

1) Description

This project contains various tools for running tests of shear estimation methods, including executables for
running shear estimation.

2) Installation

This is an Elements project, and can be built, tested, and installed in a supported environment through running:

make
make test
make install

If this is planned to be used with the pipeline runner on a LODEEN instance, it is recommended this be built and
installed in the directory /home/user/Work/Projects/SHE_CTE.

3) Dependencies

- Elements build system
- SHE_PPT
- SHE_GST
- SHE_MomentsML
- SHE_BFD
- Euclid data model bindings (in a future version)
